    "Second, while multiple works also mention recommendations to address explored limitations of RAI or RAI guidelines (e.g.",
    "Lee et al. 2021; Morley et al. 2021b; Chen et al. 2021; Peters et al. 2020), most solutions remain on a theoretical level with little guidance regarding their practical implementation.",
    "So far, only limited publications distinguish between higher level principles and concrete practices and focus on a singular domain or intervention (Harbers and Overdiek 2022).",
    "Accordingly, our work connects these philosophical critiques with practical examples addressing these limitations within AI-developing organisations.",
    "This is accomplished by highlighting examples of existing tools that facilitate the implementation of each recommendation provided."
